<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵呵，<delay20 />今天就是
期待已久的煙火大會呢～<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />到晚上7點以前還有一些時間，<delay20 />
在大會開始前，<delay8 />得先把
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />掃除之類的瑣事處理完才行！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要攤販出現在廣場上，<delay8 />
就很有祭典的氛圍呢～<pageBreak /><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對了對了，<delay20 />抽獎是晚上7點開始對吧。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />希望<tag a="110" b="4" /><delay8 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也能抽到好東西！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天好像整天都會是晴天，<delay8 />
真是一個適合放煙火的日子啊！<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在夜空中怒放的巨大花朵<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我已經等不及了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一想到煙火大會即將開幕，<delay8 />
我就興奮得無法冷靜呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，
你也跟我一樣期待煙火大會嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />太好了，原來不只我會這麼想呢～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00">我很喜歡<delay20 />煙火開始施放前，
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那種既期待<delay8 />
又緊張的感覺喔～
<anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />大會開始後，<delay8 />煙火射向空中的
聲響很令人興奮對吧～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />等等就要開始放煙火囉！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然傳統的煙火很不錯，<delay20 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是那些<delay20 />較為奇特的煙火，
我也滿喜歡的喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />煙火施放結束後的夜晚，<delay8 />
感覺比平時還要安靜呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是像這樣閉上雙眼的話，<delay20 />
眼前便會浮現在夜空中
怒放的巨大花朵喔～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那銘刻於內心的光亮與聲響<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />為了不忘記這份感動，<delay8 />
<anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我得用日記記錄下來才行，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在煙火結束以後，<delay20 />
我會覺得有那麼一點寂寞呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是，在跟<tag a="110" b="4" />
聊天後，<delay20 />寂寞的感覺
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就瞬間消失了喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 29 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今年最後的<delay20 />
煙火大會終於落幕了～<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />明年要是也能在
<tag a="110" b="33" />上
看煙火就好了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 29 00 00 00 00">雖然大會已經結束了，<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是能看到這麼多的煙火，
我感到很幸福！
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在我還對<tag a="90" b="27" />年的煙火念念不忘時，<delay20 />
內心已經開始期待起明年的煙火囉。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我這樣會<delay20 />很貪心嗎？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="012" attrib="00 00 00 29 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天的煙火大會不愧是最後壓軸，<delay8 />
相當地精采啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />大會結束後，我本來應該會感到落寞，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但現在卻神奇地有種清爽的感覺，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>